paragraphs:
[27]
The Registrar of Trademarks considered one by one each item of evidence adduced:
1. Mr. Sebag's affidavit dated January 29, 2007, along with an invoice dated October 16, 2008, and a product information card bearing the mark attached as exhibits;
2. Mr. Sebag's affidavit dated September 27, 2007, along with a warranty card as a supporting exhibit;
3. the affidavit of Mr. Elbaz, President of Fiori Canada Inc., dated September 27, 2007, along with the supporting exhibit, which was the same invoice dated October 16, 2008, as the one filed by Mr. Sebag.
